Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打算怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我上班去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不骂我呢 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样更好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…还是干脆地骂我更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须回报安鸣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学校…上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家陪我们一起收集到裤袋妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话不算数要打手腕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说不定这也是芽间的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望仁碳去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要换衣服 你出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现在我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着让人糊里糊涂的话的夏日怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间可能是想来实现愿望的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然日历已翻到初秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是夏天的怪物还住在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被逼着…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无办法地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校


Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉…汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…出汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…目光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为你说了才来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是吧 宿海! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学校了? 了不起啊! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚纪 春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 鸣子 和宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一学期不来而已 没人在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 反正也没人会注意宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 春菜你真是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 别太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说啊 爱的力量真伟大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你去了他家? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热烈 好热烈的爱啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 怎么把我跟这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「热烈」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是热昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种满是低能的家伙像动物园一样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会想来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁… 宿海! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 果然还是回去了? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说 刚才那难道就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「给我走着瞧吧」? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 就那也算? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳家的冒险～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～这边的房间是啥呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的妈妈已经去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨比这张照片要漂亮得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的照片也不太好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过芽间照相总会做V手势的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有V手势的照片可能没多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然芽间也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽间现在 总算过得还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳又会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟与安鸣的约定没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芽间…是我的幻想让我去学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有点儿想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没法…回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bentora Bentora Space People! （呼唤外星人的咒语）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:06.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bentora Bentora Space People! *N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 伙计! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙 伙计? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见? 看见什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间啊! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎呀 我还真是变厉害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我的幻想会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是奇迹的时刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我小便像这样 画出奇迹般的R的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候大概是画成δ的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 就有什么东西出现了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是你看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的视力可是能媲美奥斯曼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.25,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}此处指的是Ousmane Sankhon，\N几内亚前驻日外交官，据说视力有6.0
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 完全长成大人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大人? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 真是好女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿得什么样子? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 是她夏天常穿的白色连衣裙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间是想实现愿望才回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全心全意尽力帮忙的哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭轮到我做了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…晚饭? 不是还没到中午么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 咖喱? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮8个小时的咖喱? 我也要吃啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂仁碳 让我也…哎? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人呢? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长成大人的芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来个头 我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来真早啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 呃…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 今天是开学典礼 所以很快就结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…这是做啥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了下家政课的练习～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问都没问就乱来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饿啊 快点! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 波波别推啊! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 有那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都好想吃蒸面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳妈妈做的要好吃很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我没放葡萄干吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再多多做练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你做更更好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「更多」…你打算一直呆在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是行不行的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你也去波波那儿了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 我才不知道呢 芽间一直待在家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙说看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 难道是芽间的幽灵? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本间芽衣子～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没法交流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯…味道一般般…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是幽灵 都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛋壳混在里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 嗯…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补钙? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川…波波? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 原来你们交换过邮件地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs30\fay0.1\c&H89887D&\frz22.538\pos(702,232)}发现芽间了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现…芽间? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿来送礼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你是他女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多其他的 请慢慢挑选…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都让我陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想送给谁? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.01,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,269)}第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.01,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(514,425)}寻找芽间的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦吵死啦! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的报纸～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家可没订产经新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦没事啦 给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家在夏末一起找芽间的聚会」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间和乘凉和烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…完全不知道主旨是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 仁碳是绝对会参加的吧! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫绝对…喂! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家」也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很好玩哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也想寻找芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 带什么去好? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说嘛! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说不定这也是芽间想实现的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间可能在想「芽间也想看芽间的幽灵～」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是会用「愿望」这招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说鸣子 放学去唱卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今晚就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 计划要烧烤的 只带烤肠就行了么? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里能带的东西只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正会有人带其他东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有芽间的蒸面包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳快看 是安鸣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 仁碳! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 仁碳 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做啥 从刚才开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 再 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说仁碳 这样不好啊 要好好地集体行动才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明摔得那么华丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去的是同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹤见子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 鹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也叫了鹤见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～马尾好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外 你仔细看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了「大家」 就是指所有人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马萨拉茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.55,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}一种印度特有香茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算叫了「大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也不会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这种事 他绝对不会相信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那边稍微抬起来下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个火炉如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟营业所的大叔借的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤的东西呢? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了烤肠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要叫芽间出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这种像鬼故事的活动 需要点小道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 烧烤的材料呢? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚上不怎么吃东西 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 鹤见子只考虑自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性的女人很对我胃口啊! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为大家会带吃的来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕带了一样的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.58,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫吵! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Kheer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在印度的时候吃到的 用牛奶和香米一起煮的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像吐出来的一样～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 这个也不是拿来烧烤的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个 要不要像烤大阪烧饼那样烤烤看? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…只要烤肠就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 总算着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没火不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢 居然真的叫到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都过了多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要雕成螃蟹是怎么搞来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小螃蟹? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}安鸣要雕小螃蟹吗? 我要帮忙我要帮忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和炭是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炭本来就是用木头烧出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然的确很难点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当它回想起过去 就一口气熊熊燃烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比喻一点都不带劲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你说真的? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要我帮忙不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去烧烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有烤肠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且就切了些口子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟹? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯 芽间以前经常穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像鹤见子说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是很容易被人影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也是 现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来像芽间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽间不会穿下面这么短的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的朋友们虽然会穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是肯定…不会选白色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想穿出自己的风格的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然马上又会去跟风就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了做我自己…做得像我自己…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我说这些 是想得到什么? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是吗 真了不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听我这么回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想让你把这个随波逐流的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地骂一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳快看 是小螃蟹 是小螃蟹啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}还有小章鱼～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃! 这真是地道的德国口味! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦! 你也很识货啊 鹤见子! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 螃蟹要糊了 要糊了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎么说呢 好像甜品一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 关于芽间的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也会来帮忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事情 你相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 小螃蟹已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…相信…也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～你肯来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐仁碳 果然「超和平Busters」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超和平Busters」果然最帅了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超和平…? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没听到了呢 那个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么哪 大家都还是现役队员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎～确实是没引退呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没有哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没哭啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来 芽间也会怀念起这个来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后突然就回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么夸张的欢迎动作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什么啊 是雪集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你迟到太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫安城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 还真是好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了蔬菜和排骨来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有香草盐和橄榄油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～不愧是雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}和没用的女人们就是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你说啥! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的以为是芽间来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间她在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的啊? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在哪? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条小溪附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 仁碳! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不只你一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 什么啊? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到芽间的


